features: [Package Includes]: Set of 4 GEEORY St. Patrick's Day Pillow Covers (Insert or filler not included). These pillow covers are designed to fit 16x16 inch inserts or smaller, with the pattern exclusively featured on the front and no printing on the back. Please allow +/- 1cm tolerance as they are hand sewn and measured.

[Premium Quality & Easy Care]: Crafted from high-quality polyester, our pillow covers are built to last without any color bleeding, fading, or fraying over time. They are also machine washable for easy cleaning, making them a practical and durable addition to your home.
[Invisible Zipper Design]: Achieve a refined, seamless look with the invisible zipper closure on these festive St. Patrick's Day pillow covers.

[Instant Festive Transformation]: Liven up your festive decorations in an instant with our celebratory pillow covers. Mix and match them with other St. Patrick's Day decor to create a lively and stylish atmosphere in your home that will impress your guests.
[Satisfaction Guaranteed]: We are committed to providing exceptional customer service, and our Risk-Free 30-Day Money-Back Guarantee ensures your complete satisfaction.
